    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，c2用矩形，然后从c2 Yes到c3，c3和c4是两级PLC逻辑处理，串联后返回连到c1形成闭环？",
      "elements_involved": [
